name: NVDES - D.Y.T. Do Your Thing feat REMMI

metadata.name: NVDES - D.Y.T. (Do Your Thing) feat REMMI
metadata.description:
This is the genesis music video NFT from NVDES, the creative universe of artist, producer Josh Ocean. Belonging to no genre, the sound aesthetic of NVDES has one simple intention: To share raw creativity, energy, and high frequency vibrations with listeners in order to inspire a connection with their own creativity. 

Directed by Jenna Josepher & Jacki Huntington, this is the official music video for D.Y.T. (Do Your Thing) feat Remmi. First released in 2018 This song and video reached worldwide notoriety after the song was featured in a worldwide  campaign for Apple's iPhone X.
